HOW TO USE
1. install composer at https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md
2. run this command to install neccessary packages:
	composer global require "fxp/composer-asset-plugin:~1.0.0"
3. navigate to plrs directory and run this command to install vendor packages
	composer install
4. navigate to config directory
	4.1 edit db.php to match your database setting
	4.2 edit web.php $config['component']['mailer']['transport'] to suit your email config
